ChangeLog for gtimerge
=======================

Version 1.7.2 - 2007-03-26 (CG)
-------------
	+ producing output also if plotting out (SPR2704)
	+ GUI full implementation

Version 1.7.1 - 2004-11-10 (CG)
-------------
	+ dsslib dependency added (SPR2573)

Version 1.7 - 2003-11-06 (CG)
-----------
	+ protections changed

Version 1.6 - 2003-11-05 (CG)
-----------
	+ usedlib changed for static build


Open SPRs/SCRs:
	*none*

Version 1.5 - 2003-01-20 (UL)
-----------
	+ added 'plotmergeresult' parameter (closes SCR 102)

Version 1.4 - 2002-05-11 (GV)
-----------
	+ Requires param-2.0
	+ add set -e to test harness so that it doe not hang (on xmmps03) when
	  gtimerge fails. Also, remove return statement from shell functions.

Version 1.3 - 2001-12-07 (UL)
-----------
	+ redelivery of 1.2.2 for start of 5.3 RT

Version 1.2.2 - 2001-05-30 (UL)
